import React, { Component } from "react"; export default class About extends Component { render() { return (
About Me

A Brief Introduction

My name is Nova Wang

I have more to write later

What do I do?

A few of my talents

Strategy & Leadership

Professional team leader and team builder. Plenty of know-how in aligning organizations on the right goals. Eye for great talent.

Product Management & Design

Product-owner(ed) several internal and consumer facing apps to success at small and large companies. Know how to manage a P&L, build a vision, and execute a roadmap

Data Engineering & Analytics

Experience building sophisticated data models, insights pipelines, and reporting tools using Spark, Hive, Snowflake, Presto, Postgres, and an arsenal of viz tools.
